OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA sunny but cold start to the
OL,6,Fday. Cloud slowly increasing from the
OL,7,Fnorthwest ahead of a band of scattered
OL,8,Fshowers which will move across the
OL,9,Fregion later this afternoon. Feeling
OL,10,Fslightly warmer, but with brisk
OL,11,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showers soon clearing
OL,14,Fthis evening to leave clear skies for
OL,15,Fa while overnight. However, cloud
OL,16,Fslowly building again, with blustery
OL,17,Fshowers arriving around dawn. Less
OL,18,Fcold with brisk winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
