OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA day of sunshine and
OL,6,Fscattered blustery showers. The
OL,7,Fshowers turning heavy at times with
OL,8,Fthe odd rumble of thunder and hail.
OL,9,FFeeling cool, especially in the wind.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FStaying on the cool side with a
OL,13,Fcontinuation of sunny spells and
OL,14,Fscattered showers through Thursday and
OL,15,FFriday. Drier with lighter winds on
OL,16,FSaturday. Overnight frosts possible.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
